ABOUT THE COMMERCE CLAUSE,

00:13:35.120 --> 00:13:39.280
BECAUSE I THINK THAT PART OF
THE CHIEF'S OPINION CRYSTALLIZES

00:13:39.280 --> 00:13:44.270
THE ROBERTS COURT'S APPROACH TO
FEDERAL CASES MORE GENERALLY.

00:13:49.290 --> 00:13:51.310
I THINK THIS COURT
LIKE ITS PREDECESSOR,

00:13:51.310 --> 00:13:54.450
