FEELS VERY COMFORTABLE

00:13:54.450 --> 00:13:58.190
SECOND GUESSING CONGRESS'
LEGISLATIVE JUDGMENTS ABOUT HOW

00:13:58.190 --> 00:14:03.100
TO CARRY ITS POWERS INTO
EFFECT BASED ON THE COURT'S OWN

00:14:03.100 --> 00:14:07.870
