THERE TEND TO BE FOUR
CONSERVATIVES AND FOUR

00:49:12.260 --> 00:49:15.140
LIBERALS, AND EVERYTHING DEPENDS
ON WHERE JUSTICE KENNEDY COMES

00:49:15.140 --> 00:49:19.200
OUT, WITH UNUSUAL EXCEPTIONS
LIKE THE HEALTHCARE CASE.

00:49:19.200 --> 00:49:21.830
I THINK WHAT THIS TELLS YOU
IS THERE'S A LOT OF ROOM

00:49:21.830 --> 00:49:25.470
IN LAW FOR THE VALUE OF THE
JUDGES TO INFLUENCE THEIR

00:49:25.470 --> 00:49:26.420
INTERPRETATIONS.

00:49:26.420 --> 00:49:29.370
IT'S NOT TO SAY THAT LEGAL
INTERPRETATION IS NOTHING

00:49:29.370 --> 00:49:31.110
BUT POLITICS, BUT
IT IS TO SAY IT

00:49:31.110 --> 00:49:34.860
HAS A LOT TO DO WITH HOW
THESE THINGS ARE INTERPRETED.

00:49:34.860 --> 00:49:37.440
AND THERE ARE STUDIES SHOWING,
AND THIS IS FOLLOWING UP

00:49:37.440 --> 00:49:41.100
ON WHAT LAUREN SAID THAT ONE OF
THE CONSISTENT TAKEAWAY LINES

00:49:41.100 --> 00:49:42.270
FROM THE ROBERTS COURT.

