HE'S A LIBERAL ON
GAY RIGHTS ISSUES.

00:49:48.800 --> 00:49:51.520
HE SOMETIMES A LIBERAL ON
ISSUES INVOLVING THE DEATH

00:49:51.520 --> 00:49:52.640
PENALTY, SCHOOL PRAYER.

00:49:52.640 --> 00:49:55.070
BUT HE'S CONSERVATIVE ON
CAMPAIGN FINANCE AND RACE

00:49:55.070 --> 00:49:55.810
ISSUES.

00:49:55.810 --> 00:49:59.220
BUT ON ISSUES INVOLVING ACCESS
TO JUSTICE AND SPECIFICALLY

00:49:59.220 --> 00:50:01.470
ON THE ISSUES WHERE
THE CHAMBER OF COMMERCE

