AND THERE'S A STUDY
BY JUDGE POSNER AND A

00:50:09.470 --> 00:50:12.580
COUPLE OF ACADEMICS SHOWING
THAT THE FIVE CONSERVATIVE

00:50:12.580 --> 00:50:15.730
JUSTICES ARE FIVE OUT
OF THE TOP TEN MOST PRO

00:50:15.730 --> 00:50:18.390
CHAMBER OF COMMERCE
JUSTICES IN HISTORY.

00:50:18.390 --> 00:50:20.420
AND ROBERTS AND ALITO
ARE ONE AND TWO.

