THE COURTS DECIMATING
ACCESS TO CLASS ACTION.

00:50:26.620 --> 00:50:30.660
IT'S CUTBACK ON ACCESS TO
CONVENTIONAL CIVIL LITIGATION.

00:50:30.660 --> 00:50:32.981
IT'S CONTRACTED
ANTITRUST LIABILITY.

00:50:32.981 --> 00:50:35.480
THESE ARE A REALLY BIG DEAL AND
THEY JUST DON'T GET THE SAME

00:50:35.480 --> 00:50:39.300
HEADLINES, AND THE OUTCOMES TEND
TO BE ALONG THE SAME POLITICAL

00:50:39.300 --> 00:50:43.960
LINES THAT YOU WOULD FIND
IN CONSTITUTIONAL CASES.

